keys - GPG Key Distribution

USAGE:
    keys <developer-key>

DESCRIPTION:
    Upload GPG key to multiple key servers for distribution.
    Used for code signing and Maven deployment.

ARGUMENTS:
    developer-key
        GPG key ID to distribute (required)

KEY SERVERS:
    - mit.edu
    - pool.sks-keyservers.net
    - gnupg.net
    - keys.pgp.net
    - surfnet.nl

EXAMPLES:
    keys ABC1234567890ABCDEF1234567890ABCDEF123456
    keys 0xABC1234567890ABCDEF
